WEBVTT

00:07.898 --> 00:08.978
Sorry, Dr. Andrews.

00:09.066 --> 00:11.273
I had a patient
with some post-op arm pain.

00:11.390 --> 00:12.695
How can I help you?

00:12.940 --> 00:15.164
What's happened
to all the nurses?

00:17.244 --> 00:18.292
Hello.

00:18.380 --> 00:21.127
My name is
Dr. Shaun Murphy,

00:21.215 --> 00:23.343
surgical resident
year three.

00:23.431 --> 00:26.451
I will be assisted
by Dr. Claire Browne

00:26.539 --> 00:28.570
on today's open appendectomy.

00:28.665 --> 00:32.148
I will not be putting on my
number 7 sterile gloves myself,

00:32.274 --> 00:34.023
as I am lead surgeon.

00:34.111 --> 00:38.044
Nurse Fletch,
can you adjust the overhead light?

00:38.132 --> 00:39.880
How many degrees,
Dr. Murphy?

00:39.968 --> 00:42.615
Ah, yes.
I should be more specific.

00:42.702 --> 00:45.109
A 35-degree angle.

00:46.525 --> 00:50.484
Nurse Hawks,
please hand me the 10 blade.

00:56.050 --> 00:59.179
Straight clamp, please,
Nurse Fletch.

01:01.407 --> 01:03.055
Hello, Dr. Andrews.

01:03.158 --> 01:06.341
I'm going to try
to pretend you're not here.

01:06.593 --> 01:08.408
You have not pretended
to scrub in

01:08.495 --> 01:10.343
and may not be here
when here is there,

01:10.430 --> 01:12.326
there being O.R. 2
later today.

01:12.414 --> 01:15.015
You don't need a full
surgical team to rehearse.

01:15.102 --> 01:17.016
Some of this staff needs
to get back to their stations.

01:17.103 --> 01:18.985
No.
They can stay here.

01:19.073 --> 01:23.372
Chief Lim has assigned me
my second first surgery,

01:23.460 --> 01:25.125
and she assigned
them all to me

01:25.212 --> 01:27.260
and told me to rehearse
with all of them

01:27.347 --> 01:29.984
unless and until there's
an emergency on their floor.

01:31.355 --> 01:35.078
Dr. Browne,
please hand me the Bovie.

01:35.855 --> 01:38.216
Dr. Browne had a dental
appointment this morning.

01:38.304 --> 01:41.168
I'm doing my best to be
annoyingly caring and empathetic

01:41.256 --> 01:42.557
in her stead.

